cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the global log level to an invalid value will cause logging configuration errors and prevent proper system initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將全局日誌級別設置為無效值將導致日誌配置錯誤，並阻止正確的系統初始化。
